    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
            <p>Not published before <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>119300</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <div type="textpart" subtype="fragment" n="a">
                    <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 
                    <persName type="divine" ref="#Apollo"><name nymRef="#Ἀπόλλων"><seg part="I"><supplied reason="lost">Ἀ</supplied>πόλ<unclear>λ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ων</supplied></seg></name></persName>
                     <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="fragment" n="b">
                    <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ν</orig><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="fragment" n="c">
                    <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>κα</orig><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="fragment" n="d">
                    <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ι</orig><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
                </ab>
                </div>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> de/à Apollon <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> of/to Apollo <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> di/ad Apollo <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>At fragment a, the name of the god is certain, but it cannot be decided whether it was here at the genitive or at the dative case.</p>
	       <p>Fragment c might contain <foreign xml:lang="grc">δεκάτα</foreign> but this cannot be pushed forward.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
